		<item>
			<title>【오늘의 법조】 2024년 1월 11일</title>
			<description>&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;   &lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[법원]&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;   &lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;&lt;b&gt;▷대법원, 1부 선고&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;- 오전 10시&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;※ 아동학대 사건에서 '몰래 녹음한 파일' 증거 인정 여부 선고 (2020도1538)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;※ 일본 제철소 강제노역에 동원된 강제징용 피해자들이 일본 전범기업을 상대로 낸 손해배상청구소송 선고 (2018다47533)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;※ '故 이예람 중사 사망사건' 공보장교인 피고인들의 직권남용권리행사방해 여부 선고 (2023도178)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;&lt;b&gt;▷대법원, 3부 선고&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;- 오전 11시&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;&lt;b&gt;▷'특정경제범죄가중처벌등에관한법률위반(수재등) 등 혐의'&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;박영수 전 특검 외 1명 7차 공판&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;- 서울중앙지법, 오전 10시&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;&lt;b&gt;▷'자본시장과금융투자업에관한법률위반 등 혐의'&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;라덕연 외 2명 공판&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;- 서울남부지법, 오전 10시&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;&lt;b&gt;▷'특정경제범죄가중처벌 등에 관한 법률 위반(횡령) 등 혐의'&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;전모 씨 외 2명 우리은행 형제 횡령 사건 선고&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;- 서울고법, 오후 2시&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;&lt;b&gt;▷'업무상과실치사 등 혐의'&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;김모 씨 외 12명 가습기 살균제 사건 선고&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;- 서울고법, 오후 2시 10분&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;&lt;b&gt;▷ '강제추행치상 등 혐의'&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;박완주 의원 공판&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: -0.65px; font-family: " 맑은="" 고딕",="" "malgun="" gothic";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""&gt;- 서울남부지법, 오후 2시&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Gulim; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.65px;" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style="border-width:1px 0 0 0; border-style:dashed; border-color:lightgray;" /&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;   &lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;   &lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;[로펌]&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;p&gt;   &lt;b&gt;▷ 로스쿨생 대상 동계 실무수습&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-법무법인 바른, 1월 11일~19일&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style="border-width:2px 0 0 0; border-style:bold; border-color:lightgray;" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;   &lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[오늘의 PICK ]&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;▷ [판결] '뇌물수수 혐의' 김형준 前 부장검사, 2심도 무죄&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;뇌물수수 혐의로 1심에서 무죄가 선고된 김형준 전 부장검사에게 2심에서도 무죄가 선고됐다. 이 사건은 고위공직자범죄수사처가 출범 이후인 2021년 1월 21일 처음으로 직접 기소한 사건이다.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;   &lt;a href="https://www.lawtimes.co.kr/news/194867" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #994c00; background-color: #ffe5cc;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;☞ 기사보기 ☜&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;hr style="border-width:1px 0 0 0; border-style:dashed; border-color:lightgray;" /&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;▷ 2024 법률신문 신년 하례 세미나, 대전환기 맞은 경제·외교·정치 동향과 전망 살펴봐&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;7일 법률신문 주최로 ‘2024, 어떻게 될 것인가?’ 세미나가 열렸다. 삼성경제연구소장을 역임한 차문중 삼성글로벌리서치 사장과 윤영관 아산정책연구원 이사장, 박성민 정치평론가가 2024년 경제와 외교, 정치를 전망했다.&lt;p&gt;   &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;   &lt;a href="https://www.lawtimes.co.kr/news/194836" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #994c00; background-color: #ffe5cc;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;☞ 기사보기 ☜&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
